version_description: I've simplified the ending a bit but it's pretty much right. Not actually a dr hook song, it's a Dennis Locorriere (The Dr Hook singer) song .

This is meant to be an acoustic "Outlaw Country" version of the original 70's electric guitar, singing very high original. Drop-D gives it a bluesy flavor and allows you to sing the chorus without screeching too much. The original was very, very high.
